OL,3,CH & W agrees new loan to support
OL,4,C'ongoing stabilisation'
OL,6,FHarland & Wolff has announced it has
OL,7,Fsecured an extra #19.5 million loan
OL,8,Fthat the company hopes can support its
OL,9,F"ongoing stabilisation"
OL,11,FIt comes after the UK Government
OL,12,Frejected an application for a #200m
OL,13,Floan because of the risk to taxpayers'
OL,14,Fmoney.
OL,16,FThe total loan from the existing
OL,17,Flender now sit's at just over #109m.
