OL,6,FThe company provided the updated in a
OL,7,Fstatement to investors on Thursday. It
OL,8,Fsaid it was streamlining its
OL,9,Foperations in order to focus on its
OL,10,Fcore business that it carries out in
OL,11,FBelfast and at other locations.
OL,13,FIt is closing its Isles of Scilly
OL,14,Foperation as a result.
OL,16,FThe company also confirmed the
OL,17,Fdeparture of chief executive John Wood
OL,18,Fwho was on a leave of absence
OL,19,Ffollowing the government's rejection
OL,20,Fof support.
