OL,6,FIn a statement Harland & Wolff
OL,7,Fchairman Malcolm Groat said: "We are
OL,8,Fgrateful to our lenders in continuing
OL,9,Ftheir funding commitment to support
OL,10,FHarland & Wolff Group's ongoing
OL,11,Fstabilisation and long-term strategy
OL,12,Fobjectives.
OL,14,F"We also look forward to working with
OL,15,Fthe very experienced team from
OL,16,FRothschild & Co to help us achieve
OL,17,Fthat objective.
